  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1021">
<l>karumañ ceyavoruvaṉ kaitūvē ṉeṉṉum </l>
<l>perumaiyiṟ pīṭuṭaiya til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no higher greatness than that of one saying. I will not cease in my effort (to raise my family).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
